w goldman sachs bdc inc is a business development company specializing in middle market and mezzanine investment in private companies it seeks to make capital appreciation through direct originations of secured debt senior secured debt junior secured debt including first lien first lienlastout unitranche and second lien debt unsecured debt including mezzanine debt and to a lesser extent investments in equities the fund primarily invests in united states it seeks to invest between  million and  million in companies with ebitda between  million and  million annually  west streetnew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwgoldmansachsbdccomcontentgsamusenbdchomepagehtml key executives for goldman sachs bdc inc mr brendan m mcgovern chief executive officer and president mr jonathan lamm chief financial officer and treasurer age  mr jon yoder chief operating officer age  mr david yu head of research and executive vice president age  ms katherine schneider head of investor relations compensation as of fiscal year  goldman sachs bdc inc key developments goldman sachs bdc inc announces second quarter dividend payable on july   may   goldman sachs bdc inc announced a second quarter dividend of  per share payable to shareholders of record as of june   payable on july   goldman sachs bdc inc announces unaudited consolidated financial results for the first quarter ended march   may   goldman sachs bdc inc announced unaudited consolidated financial results for the first quarter ended march   for the quarter the company’s total investment income was  against  a year ago the increase in investment income over the quarter was primarily driven by higher interest income including higher prepayment income partially offset by a decline in other income net investment income before taxes was  against  a year ago net investment income after taxes was  against  a year ago net realized and unrealized losses were  against  a year ago net increase in net assets resulting from operatio